imdb.plot outline: Major League Baseball All-Star Giancarlo Stanton joins sports yoga instructor Kent Katich for four dynamic, athletic yoga practices designed to build strength, power and balance. Katich has coached some of the best athletes in the world, using yoga to elevate their physical performance and mental edge.
imdb.title: Gaiam: Athletic Yoga, Yoga for Power with Giancarlo Stanton
